product.title: Kawaii Anime Aesthetics Large Mouse Pad
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • The missing touch to your desk

    A must-have for anime lovers and those who want to add a touch of cutesy lo-fi vibe to their decor. These mouse pads will revitalize the look and feel of your deskspace, making you smile whenever you see it.

    Long mousepads expand the working area of your computer to enhance your gaming and working experience at your desk. Our specially designed mousepads give you a smooth, seamless surface for accurate and precise movements with no jitters. Choose between 24 anime designs to match your aesthetics!


    Perfect addition to your office, home and even ideal for gifts

    This flexible and durable mouse mat is smooth and soft to the touch making gaming and working at your desk a more comfortable and enjoyable experience.

    Features

    🌸 24 Anime Aesthetic designs to choose from
    🌸 4 sizes available
    🌸 3mm thick 
    🌸 Rubber back material to prevent slipping

  • Do you ship worldwide? Yes, we ship to over 300 countries and are proud to provide free shipping to the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, and many countries in Europe.

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, some countries within the EU, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.


    Packaging time: 1-5 Business days

    Shipping time: 5-20 Business days
